                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "that U-boats would sink on sight all ships in the waters around Britain and France"
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "helping the United States seize territory in Mexico and neighboring countries"
                },
